Speedbreaker looks at the confused Stratus, then grabs him, and flies up
towards the bush. "This should be interesting, we dont want to miss any of
it." he flies for a ways, and then stays hovering, looking at Motormaster
arrived.

Motormaster transforms, and gets out his Cyclone gun. "You obviously cant
cut it, therefore you cant be Megatron" he screams. Megatron then emerges
from a bush behind him, screaming with rage, and lock Motormaster from
behind. Motormaster strugles, but cannot break Megatron's grip, he then
elbows Megatron in the head. Megatron decides to grab between his legs, and
hoist Motormaster up over his head, and throws him straight up in the air.
Motormaster screams, as he starts to head towards the ground at a high
speed. Making hard impact with the ground, Motormaster then rolls over, and
sees he is on the edge of a cliff, looking down at the Hudson bay. At the
bottom of the cliff, and a bit off, is the Decepticons ship. He gets up and
readies himself for Megatron.
